billEvents.eventText: REFERRED TO CORPORATIONS, AUTHORITIES AND COMMISSIONS

title: Relates to blighted property and blighted areas; repealer
summary: Establishes what is and what is not blighted property and blighted areas.
lawSection: New York State Urban Development Corporation Act
actClause: AN ACT to amend the New York state urban development corporation act, in relation to blighted property and blighted areas; and to repeal certain provisions of such act relating thereto
